%20Leaving%20Ground%20Mid-Way%20During%20Batting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20eight-wicket%20win%20over%20Ireland%20in%20their%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20opener%20on%20Wednesday%20got%20soured%20a%20bit%20as%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20trudged%20off%20the%20field%20mid-way%20during%20batting.%20Rohit%20left%20the%20ground%20after%20suffering%20a%20blow%20on%20his%20upper%20arm%20from%20a%20delivery%20bowled%20by%20pacer%20Josh%20Little%20at%20Nassau%20County%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20in%20New%20York.%20Before%20retiring%20hurt%2C%20Rohit%20scored%2052%20off%2037%20balls%20with%20the%20help%20of%20four%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes%20to%20give%20India%20a%20perfect%20launching%20pad%20to%20chase%20down%20a%20paltry%20target%20of%2097.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20got%20hit%20on%20his%20upper%20arm%20on%20the%20second%20ball%20of%20the%20ninth%20over.%20The%20injury%20eventually%20forced%20him%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20field%20after%20the%20final%20ball%20of%20the%2010th%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20for%20India%20was%20that%20the%20injury%20was%20not%20serious.%20Rohit%20revealed%20about%20it%20after%20the%20game.%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20just%20a%20little%20sore%20(the%20arm)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20India%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20India's%20innings%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20too%20copped%20a%20blow%20on%20his%20elbow%20on%20the%20first%20ball%20of%20the%2011th%20over.%20That%20delivery%20was%20also%20bowled%20by%20Josh%20Little.%20Pant%2C%20however%2C%20continued%20his%20innings%20after%20receiving%20some%20treatment%20from%20the%20physio%20and%20finished%20off%20the%20match%20with%20a%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surface%20of%20Nassau%20County%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%2C%20where%20the%20India%20vs%20Ireland%20match%20was%20played%2C%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20for%20its%20vicious%20bounce%20while%20the%20extremely%20slow%20outfield%20was%20also%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20critics'%20fury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%20it%20at%20the%20toss%20as%20well.%20Quite%20unsure%20of%20what%20to%20expect%20from%20the%20pitch.%20Not%20aware%20on%20what%20it%20is%20to%20play%20like%20on%20a%20pitch%20that's%20five%20months%20old.%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20wicket%20settled%20down%20even%20when%20we%20batted%20second%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20enough%20for%20the%20bowlers.%20That's%20pretty%20much%20what%20you%20gotta%20do.%20Try%20to%20hit%20those%20lengths%20consistently.%20All%20these%20guys%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20Test%20cricket.%20Arshdeep%20is%20the%20only%20guy%20who%20hasn't.%20His%20two%20wickets%20upfront%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20are%20set%20to%20take%20on%20Pakistan%20at%20the%20same%20venue%20on%20June%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20from%20the%20pitch%20to%20be%20honest.%20We%20will%20prepare%20as%20if%20the%20conditions%20are%20going%20to%20be%20like%20this%20(for%20Pakistan%20game).%20This%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20kind%20of%20game%20where%20all%20XI%20of%20us%20will%20need%20to%20contribute.%20It%20was%20scratchy%2C%20but%20good%20to%20spend%20some%20time%20in%20the%20middle%20and%20understand%20what%20kind%20of%20shots%20to%20play%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20concluded%20the%20India%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717635180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F4hcmmou_rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_05_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Frohit-sharma-provides-