ls%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%E2%84%A0%20Visa%C2%AE%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20Citi%20has%20released%20an%20updated%20version%20of%20the%20Premier%20Card%20in%20the%20Citi%20Strata%20Premier%E2%84%A0%20Card%2C%20I'm%20happy%20with%20my%20choice%20to%20switch%20%E2%80%94%20the%20updated%20card%20improves%20some%20of%20what%20I%20didn't%20like%20about%20it%2C%20but%20not%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwells-fargo-launches-autograph-journey-announces-travel-transfer-partners-2024-3%5C%22%3EAutograph%20Journey%20card%20launched%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%202024%20and%20has%20already%20made%20a%20big%20splash%20with%20superior%20category%20bonuses%20and%20a%20small%20but%20mighty%20list%20of%20transfer%20partners%2C%20three%20of%20which%20it%20has%20in%20common%20with%20Citi.%20With%20a%20similar%20welcome%20bonus%20and%20the%20same%20%2495%20annual%20fee%2C%20the%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%20Card%20is%20better%20for%20me%20than%20my%20Citi%20Premier%20Card.%20Here's%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Better%20category%20bonuses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%20Card's%20bonus%20categories%20better%20suit%20my%20spending%20habits%20than%20the%20Citi%20Premier%20bonuses%20did.%20I%20was%20happy%20earning%203X%20points%20on%20air%20travel%2C%20hotels%2C%20restaurants%2C%20gas%20stations%2C%20and%20supermarkets.%20However%2C%20the%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%20offers%20higher%20bonuses%20on%20key%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20I'll%20earn%205X%20points%20on%20hotels%2C%204X%20on%20airlines%2C%20and%203X%20on%20all%20other%20travel%20and%20dining.%20Since%20travel%20is%20a%20big%20spending%20category%20for%20me%2C%20I'd%20much%20rather%20earn%20four%20or%20five%20points%20per%20dollar%20in%20those%20categories%20than%20have%203X%20on%20gas%20and%20groceries.%20The%20Autograph%20Journey%20card%20will%20help%20me%20earn%20more%20points%20beyond%20flights%20and%20hotel%2C%20especially%20since%20the%203X%20travel%20category%20includes%20rental%20cars%2C%20cruise%20lines%2C%20and%20travel%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Valuable%20travel%20protections%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20does%20the%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%20earn%20generous%20rewards%20on%20some%20of%20my%20biggest%20expenses%2C%20but%20it%20also%20offers%20an%20important%20feature%20the%20Citi%20Premier%20Card%20lacked%3A%20travel%20and%20purchase%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftravel-insurance-vs-credit-card%5C%22%3Ecredit%20card%20travel%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20recoup%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20otherwise%20nonrefundable%20travel.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20recouped%20over%20%241%2C000%20in%20airfare%20when%20my%20brother%20got%20COVID-19%20and%20had%20to%20cancel%20his%20trip%20to%20London.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Famerican-express-platinum-credit-card-review%5C%22%3EAmex%20Platinum%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20trip%20interruption%20insurance%2C%20which%20reimbursed%20the%20expense%20after%20I%20submitted%20all%20the%20required%20paperwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20got%20into%20an%20accident%20involving%20my%20rental%20car%2C%20and%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Famex-gold-card-review%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Express%C2%AE%20Gold%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E%20covered%20the%20%244%2C500%20in%20damages%20involved.%20For%20years%2C%20I%20couldn't%20charge%20my%20travel%20expenses%20to%20my%20Citi%20Premier%2C%20despite%20the%203X%20category%20bonus%2C%20because%20it%20lacked%20this%20important%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%20the%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%20Card%2C%20I%20can%20enjoy%20elevated%20earnings%20on%20travel%20while%20receiving%20lost%20luggage%20reimbursement%2C%20trip%20cancellation%20and%20interruption%20insurance%2C%20auto%20rental%20collision%20damage%20waiver%2C%20and%20travel%20accident%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Cellphone%20protection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%20Card%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20credit%20cards%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards-with-cell-phone-protection%5C%22%3Ecellphone%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20provides%20up%20to%20%241%2C000%20in%20coverage%20against%20damage%20or%20theft%20up%20to%20twice%20a%20year.%20The%20%2425%20deductible%20is%20reasonable%20compared%20to%20other%20credit%20cards%20that%20have%20deductibles%20upwards%20of%20%24100%20per%20claim.%20Even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcapital-one-venture-x-rewards-credit-card-review%5C%22%3ECapital%20One%20Venture%20X%20Rewards%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E%20charges%20%2450%20and%20limits%20coverage%20to%20%24800%20per%20claim%2C%20making%20the%20Autograph%20Journey%20Card%20a%20better%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20requirement%20for%20cellphone%20protection%20coverage%20is%20charging%20your%20monthly%20bill%20to%20the%20card.%20That's%20easy%20for%20me%20since%20the%20card%20earns%20the%20same%201%20point%20per%20dollar%20as%20the%20Citi%20Strata%20Premier%E2%84%A0%20Card.%20With%20such%20a%20valuable%20benefit%20as%20an%20incentive%2C%20I'd%20much%20rather%20use%20the%20Autograph%20Journey%20card%20to%20pay%20my%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20An%20easier%20airline%20credit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%20Card%20has%20a%20%2495%20annual%20fee%2C%20partially%20offset%20by%20a%20%2450%20airline%20fee%20credit.%20This%20credit%20is%20much%20more%20flexible%20and%20easier%20to%20use%20than%20Citi%20Strata%20Premier's%20%24100%20hotel%20credit.%20The%20airline%20credit%20requires%20a%20minimum%20%2450%20charge%2C%20which%20isn't%20hard%20to%20meet%20if%20you're%20paying%20for%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Citi%20Strata%20Premier's%20%24100%20hotel%20credit%20only%20applies%20to%20bookings%20of%20%24500%20or%20more.%20It's%20restricted%20to%20hotels%20booked%20through%20Citi's%20proprietary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fciti-thankyou-travel-portal%5C%22%3EThankYou%20travel%20portal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Booking%20through%20a%20third-party%20portal%20like%20this%20often%20means%20you%20won't%20earn%20points%20with%20your%20hotel%20loyalty%20program%20or%20get%20access%20to%20elite%20member%20benefits.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20credit%20applies%20after%20taxes%2C%20limiting%20your%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey's%20%2450%20airline%20credit%20is%20easier%20to%20use%20and%20more%20versatile.%20I%20know%20I'll%20use%20it%20every%20year%2C%20while%20Citi%20Strata%20Premier's%20%24100%20hotel%20credit%20often%20went%20unused%20because%20I%20prefer%20to%20book%20my%20hotel%20stays%20directly%20to%20reap%20the%20rewards%20and%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Access%20to%20the%20Visa%20Signature%20Luxury%20Hotel%20Collection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Visa%20Signature%20Card%2C%20the%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Journey%20provides%20access%20to%2024%2F7%20concierge%20services%20and%20the%20Visa%20Signature%20Luxury%20Hotel%20Collection.%20The%20former%20isn't%20a%20benefit%20I'll%20actually%20use%2C%20but%20the%20Luxury%20Hotel%20Collection%20offers%20substantial%20savings%20and%20perks%20on%20hotel%20bookings.%20Cardholders%20receive%20valuable%20benefits%20at%20select%20hotels%2C%20including%20the%20third%20or%20fourth%20night%20free%2C%20on-site%20dining%20and%20resort%20credits%2C%20automatic%20room%20upgrades%2C%20complimentary%20breakfast%20for%20two%2C%20and%20other%20valuable%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20900%20hotels%20participate%20in%20the%20Luxury%20Hotel%20Collection%2C%20including%20popular%20brands%20like%20Kimpton%2C%20Waldorf%20Astoria%2C%20Park%20Hyatt%2C%20and%20more.%20It's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20secure%20extra%20perks%20at%20hotels%20where%20I%20don't%20have%20elite%20status%20with%20the%20chain.%20Visa%20Signature%20offers%20the%20best%20rate%20guarantee%2C%20so%20in%20theory%2C%20I%20won't%20pay%20a%20higher%20rate%20for%20these%20benefits%20than%20if%20I%20were%20to%20book%20directly.%20The%20Citi%20Strata%20Premier%20Card%20offers%20nothing%20similar%20to%20the%20Luxury%20Hotel%20Collection%2C%20so%20the%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Card%20is%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-favorite-credit-card-does-everything-better-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717620735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e4b7f14fb5b23cc5f62e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-favorite-credit-card-does-everything-better-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20the%20Wells%20Fargo%20Autograph%20Card%20launched%20in%20March%2C%20I%20decided%20it%20was%20time%20to%20make%20the%20switch%20and%20use%20it%20as%20my%20primary%20credit%20card.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ariana%40pointchaser.com%20(Ariana%20Arghandewal)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-favorite-credit-card-does-everything-better-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Warfare%20experts%20rate%2012%20'Game%20of%20Thrones'%20scenes%20for%20realism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2Fccfqit8h-jZbcmOYf.html%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Warfare%20experts%20rate%2012%20'Game%20of%20Thrones'%20scenes%20for%20realism%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERoel