ing%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20today.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20caveat.%20%26quot%3BThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20continue%20to%20resist%20the%20fascist%20rule...%20We%20will%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20at%20the%20appropriate%20time%20to%20realise%20the%20people's%20desire%20not%20to%20be%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20reading%20out%20a%20statement%20adopted%20by%20all%20the%20alliance%20partners%20after%20a%20strategy%20session%20at%20his%20Delhi%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thinly%20veiled%20reference%20was%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20initial%20idea%20of%20prising%20away%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20chief%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister-elect%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20two%20erstwhile%20allies%20signed%20up%20the%20NDA%20earlier%20today%20with%20formal%20letters%20of%20support%2C%20pouring%20cold%20water%20on%20the%20Opposition's%20hopes%20of%20a%20realignment%20that%20would%20put%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20on%20the%20driver's%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20sources%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20could%20send%20feelers%20to%20erstwhile%20allies%20Mr%20Kumar%20and%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20and%20explore%20options.%20Mr%20Naidu%20was%20earlier%20part%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20a%20acquired%20a%20reputation%20of%20sorts%20for%20his%20frequent%20flip%20flops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%20initially%20made%20public%20by%20INDIA%20ally%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%20But%20Mr%20Kharge%20had%20been%20circumspect%2C%20saying%20they%20would%20consult%20allies%20to%20decide%20the%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20evening%2C%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20strategy%20session%20held%20at%20his%20home%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20issued%20an%20open%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20welcomes%20all%20parties%20which%20share%20its%20fundamental%20commitment%20to%20the%20values%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Preamble%20to%20our%20Constitution%20and%20to%20its%20many%20provisions%20for%20economic%2C%20social%20and%20political%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%2C%20riding%20a%20high%20that%20came%20after%20a%20decade%2C%20has%20demanded%20the%20resignation%20of%20PM%20Modi%2C%20declaring%20that%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20people%20want%20him%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mandate%20is%20decisively%20against%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20against%20him%20and%20the%20substance%20and%20style%20of%20his%20politics.%20It%20is%20a%20huge%20political%20loss%20for%20him%20personally%20apart%20from%20being%20a%20clear%20moral%20defeat%20as%20well.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20determined%20to%20subvert%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20at%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20constituents%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc%20thank%20the%20people%20of%20India%20for%20the%20overwhelming%20support%20received%20by%20our%20alliance.%20The%20people's%20mandate%20has%20given%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20their%20politics%20of%20hate%2C%20corruption%20and%20deprivation.%20This%20is%20a%20political%20and%20moral%20defeat%20of%20Prime%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FoWyQSrxWBR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FoWyQSrxWBR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1798379846101524643%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20240%20seats%20and%20293%20with%20its%20allies%20--%2028%20of%20them%20are%20contributions%20of%20Mr%20Kumar%20and%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Chief%20Minister-elect%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20with%20a%20spectacular%20comeback%20under%20his%20belt.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20232%20seats%2C%2099%20from%20Congress%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717605480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F5gcs56i_mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_05_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-electon-2024-results-after-india-meet-mallikarjun-kharges-right-step-at-right-time-promise-5825987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20for%20now%2C%20will%20sit%20in%20the%20opposition%20benches%2C%20even%20though%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20%26quot%3Bsubverting%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-electon-2024-results-after-india-meet-mallikarjun-kharges-right-step-at-right-time-promise-5825987%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-electon-2024-results-after-india-meet-mallikarjun-kharges-right-step-at-right-time-promise-5825987%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-electon-2024-results-after-india-meet-mallikarjun-kharges-right-step-at-right-time-promise-5825987%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bulls%20stage%20Rs%2017%20trn%20recovery%20as%20worries%20about%20NDA%20forming%20govt%20ease%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717604812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F01%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1717210609-5525.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstock-market-news%2Fbulls-stage-rs-17-trn-recovery-as-worries-a