ument%20outside%3B%20as%20we%20looked%20out%2C%20we%20could%20see%20where%20the%20neighbour%20was%20shooting%20the%20other%20neighbour%2C%20who%20unfortunately%20passed%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20witness%20told%20Costa%20Rica%20English%20newspaper%20the%20%3Cem%3ETico%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZamora%20discharged%20his%20weapon%20multiple%20additional%20times%20(nine%20rounds%20according%20to%20reports)%20at%20Mendoza.%20The%20force%20of%20the%20gunfire%20caused%20Mendoza%20to%20fall%20backwards.%20The%20gunman's%20wife%20then%20intervened%2C%20pulling%20him%20away%20from%20the%20scene.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Mendoza's%20partner%20reacted%20with%20screams%20of%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20he%20was%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20other%20neighbour%20continued%20to%20shoot%20him%20without%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20witness%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20indicate%20a%20history%20of%20animosity%20between%20Zamora%20and%20Mendoza%2C%20suggesting%20tensions%20had%20been%20building%20for%20some%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20bothered%20him%20every%20time%20he%20(Otto)%20went%20out%2C%20bothered%20his%20children%20and%20wife%2C%20he%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20regarding%20Mr%20Otto's%20nationality%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20unidentified%20witness%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMendoza%20had%20moved%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20from%20his%20native%20Nicaragua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20even%20questioned%20how%20it%20was%20possible%20that%20a%20Nicaraguan%20could%20live%20in%20a%20place%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20witness%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMendoza%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20at%20the%20scene%20despite%20other%20neighbours%20trying%20to%20save%20him.%20He%20suffered%20gunshot%20wounds%20to%20the%20thorax%20and%20legs%2C%20the%20Tico%20Times%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20Judicial%20Investigation%20Department%20(OIJ).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Mendoza's%20relatives%20blasted%20local%20law%20enforcement%20for%20not%20doing%20anything%20to%20stop%20the%20feuding%20neighbours'%20continuing%20disagreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20always%20had%20problems.%20It%20had%20been%20going%20on%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20They%20even%20sued%20him%2C%20and%20nobody%20did%20anything.%20Neither%20the%20police%20force%20nor%20the%20OIJ%20acted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mourning%20relative%20said%20to%20the%20newspaper.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20happened%2C%20only%20that%20they%20argued.%20I%20do%20not%20understand%20that.%20How%20is%20that%20possible%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20took%20Zamora%20into%20custody%20following%20the%20altercation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeighbours%20reported%20having%20no%20knowledge%20of%20Zamora%20possessing%20a%20gun%20and%20previously%20urged%20both%20parties%20to%20resolve%20their%20differences%20peacefully%20for%20the%20good%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tragic%20event%20earlier%20this%20year%20saw%20a%20Las%20Vegas%20pastor%20gunned%20down%20by%20a%20deranged%20neighbour%20in%20his%20driveway%20after%20filing%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20homeowners'%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Junio%20opened%20fire%2C%20fatally%20striking%20Nick%20Davi%20in%20the%20stomach%20as%20his%20traumatized%20children%20witnessed%20the%20scene%20from%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20shooting%20the%20father%2C%20Junio%20aimed%20the%20weapon%20at%20Sarah%2C%20Davi's%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717597200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Frjtc78m_costa-rica-man-shoots-neighbour_625x300_05_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-man-shoots-neighbour-9-times-in-front-of-family-after-heated-argument-5825306%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tragically%2C%20the%20situation%20takes%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%20as%20the%20man%20with%20the%20gun%20fires%20at%20his%20neighbour%2C%20striking%20him%20multiple%20times.%22%2C%22author%22%