0Rejected%26quot%3B%3A%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20Chief%20On%20Big%20Poll%20Defeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fk-annamalai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EK%20Annamalai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%2C%20has%20said%20the%20party's%20poor%20showing%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20does%20not%20constitute%20%26quot%3Brejection%20of%20Hindutva%20brand%20of%20politics%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20will%20introspect%20and%20learns%20lessons%20from%20what%20went%20wrong.%20I%20am%20unhappy%20about%20no%20victory%20for%20BJP%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu...%20we%20got%20many%20hits%20and%20misses.%20But%20Tamil%20Nadu%20results%20are%20not%20a%20rejection%20of%20Hindutva%20brand%20of%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20dismissed%20suggestions%20the%20party%20may%20have%20fared%20better%20had%20it%20retained%20ties%20with%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20one%20of%20two%20major%20parties%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Dravidian-focused%20political%20landscape.%20%C2%A0The%20Tamil%20party%20-%20also%20routed%2C%20and%20which%20also%20lost%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%202021%20Assembly%20poll%20as%20a%20BJP%20ally%20-%20quit%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20Mr%20Annamalai%20criticised%20party%20icons%20J%20Jayalalithaa%20and%20CN%20Annadurai.%20The%20under-fire%20BJP%20leader%20had%20then%20refused%20to%20back%20down%20and%20declared%20that%20going%20solo%20would%20strengthen%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlliance%20with%20AIADMK%20didn't%20work%20in%20the%20past...%20no%20point%20in%20looking%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Annamalai%20also%20junked%20talk%20of%20the%20BJP's%20underwhelming%20show%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20the%20party%20has%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20three%20polls%2C%20failed%20to%20cross%20the%20272-majority%20mark%20on%20its%20own%2C%20and%20must%20actively%20rely%20on%20NDA%20partners%2C%20including%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20for%20a%20third%20term%20Saturday)%20is%20not%20weakened%20by%20a%20coalition.%20Modiji%20is%20democratic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Tamil%20leader%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20muscular%20nationalist%20model%20has%20traditionally%20struggled%20with%20Tamil%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202014%20poll%2C%20while%20most%20of%20India%20was%20enticed%20by%20the%20'Modi%20wave'%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20largely%20unmoved.%20The%20BJP%20got%20just%20one%20of%20its%2039%20seats%3B%20Pon%20Radhakrishnan%20won%20from%20Kanniyakumari.%20In%202019%20the%20BJP%20was%20routed%20-%20zero%20seats%20and%20the%20vote%20share%20fell%20to%203.6%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202024%20election%20Mr%20Modi%20made%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20visits%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20neighbouring%20Kerala%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20identified%20the%20southern%20states%20(and%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh)%20as%20key%20in%20helping%20break%20the%20400-seat%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20high-profile%20campaign%2C%20which%20included%20Amit%20Shah%20also%20making%20appearances%2C%20failed%20to%20produce%20results.%20The%20BJP%20was%20blanked%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%20a%20second%20straight%20election%2C%20although%20it%20came%20a%20distant%20second%20in%2010%C2%A0seats%20and%20its%20vote%20share%20(including%20allies)%20rose%20to%2010.24%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20local%20ally%20-%20the%20Pattali%20Makkal%20Katchi%20-%20was%20leading%20the%20Dharmapuri%20seat%2C%20but%20that%20was%20snapped%20up%20by%20the%20ruling%20DMK's%20A%20Mani%20after%20a%20close%20fight.%20That%20was%20about%20as%20good%20as%20it%20got%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Annamalai%2C%20contesting%20from%20Coimbatore%2C%20was%20thumped%20by%20the%20DMK's%20Ganpathy%20Rajkumar%20by%20nearly%201.2%20lakh%20votes.%20Another%20high-profile%20BJP%20candidate%2C%20ex-Telangana%20Governor%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%2C%20lost%20the%20Chennai%20(South)%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%2C%20which%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20orchestrated%20a%20clean%20sweep.%20The%20party%20won%2022%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20got%20nine%2C%20and%20smaller%20outfits%20picked%20up%20the%20rest.%20And%20with%20the%20Congress%20also%20winning%20Puducherry%2C%20the%20DMK-led%20front%20completed%20a%20neat%2040%2F40%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717595880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkll2jmh_k-annamalai-1200-_625x300_12_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-k-annamalai-hindutva-politics-not-rejected-tamil-nadu-bjp-chief-on-big-poll-defeat-5824839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22K%20Annamalai%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%2C%20has%20said%20the%20party's%20poor%20showing%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20does%20not%20constitute%20%26quot%3Brejection%20of%20Hindutva%20brand%20of%20politics%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-k-annamalai-hindutva-politics-not-rejected-tamil-nadu-bjp-chief-on-big-poll-defeat-5824839%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-k-annamalai-hindutva-politics-not-rejected-tamil-nadu-bjp-chief-on-big-poll-defeat-5824839%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-k-annamalai-hindutva-politics-not-rejected-tamil-nadu-bjp-chief-on-big-poll-defeat-5824839%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Arrogance%2C%20EVMs%20And%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3A%20Key%20Lessons%20From%20Election%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2F9pvq8ncs_narendra-modi-afp-file-photo_625x300_12_November_18.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20men%20are%20most%20sure%20and%20arrogant%20they%20are%20commonly%20most%20mistaken%2C%20giving%20views%20to%20passion%20without%20that%20proper%20deliberation%20which%20alone%20can%20secure%20them%20from%20the%20grossest%20absurdities.%26quot%3B%20Philosopher%20David%20Hume%20could%20just%20as%20well%20be%20writing%20about%20the%20results%20of%20the%202024%20general%20election%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArrogance%2C%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20this%20election%2C%20is%20twice%20cursed.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20produce%20%26quot%3Bignorance%20by%20silencing%20others%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20also%20breeds%20%26quot%3Bself-delusion%20in%20the%20arrogant%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20explained%20more%20recently%20by%20Alessandra%20Tanesini.%20In%20Greek%20tragedy%2C%20arrogance%20was%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20essential%20flaws%20of%20the%20tragic%20hero.%20In%20our%20times%2C%20however%2C%20heroism%20itself%20is%20a%20casualty%20of%20arrogance.%20This%20election%20has%20been%20a%20moment%20of%20reckoning%20for%20everyone%20who%20wore%20arrogance%20as%20a%20second%20skin.%20It%20won't%20be%20hyperbolic%20to%20say%20that%20the%20humble%2C%20vulnerable%2C%20taken-for-granted%20voter%20had%20the%20last%20word%2C%20delivering%20a%20coup%20de%20grace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20remember%2C%20however%2C%20that%20arrogance%20was%20not%20the%20sole%20domain%20of%20one%20or%20more%20political%20parties%20in%20this%20election%20season.%20All%20stakeholders%20are%20guilty%20of%20displaying%20different%20signs%20and%20shades%20of%20it.%20Here%20are%20some%20lessons%20for%20those%20who%20badly%20need%20to%20relearn%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Never%20Take%20The%20Voter%20For%20Granted.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20voter%20in%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%20remains%20extremely%20vulnerable%2C%20putting%20her%20neck%20on%20the%20line%20for%20the%20favourite%20candidate.%20Respect%20that.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20paid%20the%20price%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20for%20thinking%20of%20its%20voter%20base%20as%20captive%20and%20this%20time%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20same%20dock.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Do%20Not%20Raise%20The%20Electoral%20Pitch%20To%20Uncomfortable%20Levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20begin%20with%2C%20the%20expectations%20were%20unrealistic%20for%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20and%20the%20BJP.%20400%2B%20and%20295%20scores%20demanded%20an%20almost%2090%25%20strike%20rate%20in%20the%20total%20number%20of%20seats%20contested.%20The%20BJP%20particularly%20set%20itself%20up%20for%20failure%20by%20making%20this%20grandiose%20claim%20which%20also%20ended%20up%20irking%20and%20intimidating%20its%20core%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Always%20Take%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Seriously!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20legendary%20unpredictability%20of%20UP%20that%20brought%20back%20the%20fight%20in%20the%202024%20general%20election.%20None%20of%20the%20exit%20polls%20or%20electoral%20assessments%20of%20parties%20captured%20the%20surprise%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20sprung%20up%20in%20this%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Move%20Away%20From%20The%20Cult%20Of%20Personality.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20voters%20are%20vulnerable%20and%20punishing%20in%20equal%20measure.%20They%20may%20not%20know%20who%20or%20what%20they%20want%2C%20but%20they%20certainly%20know%20what%2Fwho%20to%20reject.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Referendums%20Are%20Risky.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERural%20distress%20-%20despite%20social%20welfare%20schemes%20-%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20deciding%20factors%20in%20this%20election.%20Jobless%20growth%2C%20flawed%20schemes%20like%20Agniveer%20(short-term%20military%20recruitment)%2C%20the%20heavy-handed%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20political%20opponents%2C%20and%20an%20uneasy%20feeling%20around%20the%20potential%20absolute%20majority%20made%20the%20voters%20look%20for%20other%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Collaborationism%20Compromises%20Credibility.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedia%2C%20policy%20wonks%2C%20scholars%20and%20intellectuals%20not%20even%20pretending%20to%20be%20neutral%20need%20to%20soul%20search.%20Secondhand%20arrogance%20has%20much%20worse%20consequences%20when%20the%20time%20of%20churning%20comes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Cultural%20Snobbery%20Won't%20Save%20Anyone.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20one%20region%20or%20culture%20as%20superior%20to%20others%20is%20almost%20always%20a%20temptation%20to%20the%20fates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Accept%20That%20Predicting%20Voter%20Behaviour%20Is%20Next%20To%20Impossible.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20analysts%2C%20strategists%2C%20and%20journalists%20who%20changed%20their%20predictions%2C%20theories%20and%20analyses%20faster%20than%20they%20blinked%20on%20the%20counting%20day.%20They%20are%20fooling%20nobody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20Bureaucrats%20need%20to%20find%20the%20drawing%20board%20and%20go%20back%20to%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIngratiating%20oneself%20with%20the%20political%20players%20is%20damaging%20to%20your%20career%20and%20credibility.%20When%20the%20tables%20turn%2C%20Comeuppance%20may%20not%20use%20a%20white%20towel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%20Have%20Faith.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrogance%20of%20the%20faithless%20is%20the%20worst%20kind.%20It%20often%20masks%20laziness%20and%20incompetence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20last%20lesson%20is%20for%20all%20those%20political%20leaders%2C%20their%20supporters%20and%20even%20non-committed%20voters%20who%20willingly%20furthered%20the%20propaganda%20around%20allegedly%20manipulated%20EVMs.%20The%20present%20verdict%20is%20a%20stern%20reminder%20to%20all%20the%20naysayers%20that%20a%20selective%20belief%20in%20systems%20and%20institutions%20is%20a%20zero-sum%20game.%20Political%20leaders%20who%20had%20started%20questioning%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20verdict%20even%20before%20it%20was%20out%20should%20be%20ashamed%20of%20their%20manipulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20discredit%20the%20process%2C%20you%20also%20discredit%20the%20participants%2C%20the%20voters.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20the%202024%20elections%20were%20free%20of%20all%20glitches.%20The%20election%20commission's%20silence%20over%20violations%20of%20all%20codes%20of%20conduct%20will%20not%20be%20forgotten.%20Attempts%20at%20vitiating%20the%20atmosphere%20through%20conspiracy%20theories%20or%20acts%20of%20violence%20won't%20be%20forgotten%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20the%20victims%20of%20arrogance%20stay%20silent%20can%20often%20be%20misconstrued%20as%20acceptance.%20For%20convenience%2C%20let%20us%20blame%20this%20misunderstanding%20on%20Plato.%20In%20Cratylus%2C%20Socrates%20addresses%20Cratylus%20thus%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20shall%20assume%20that%20your%20silence%20gives%20consent%26quot%3B.%20An%20arrogant%20person%20often%20lives%20in%20a%20make-believe%20world%20-%20believing%20in%20his%20invincibility%20and%20desirability.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20it%20is%20injurious%20to%20physical%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20professional%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20we%20are%20back%20to%20normal%20after%20two%20anomalous%20elections%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20Coalition%20governments%20are%20nothing%20new%20to%20India.%20So-called%20invincible%20brands%20have%20taken%20a%20beating.%20One%20hopes%20these%20results%20will%20usher%20in%20an%20era%20where%20electoral%20arrogance%20will%20give%20way%20to%20humility%20and%20collaborative%20governance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717594320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2F9pvq8ncs_narendra-modi-afp-file-photo_625x300_12_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Farrogance-evms-and-uttar-pradesh-election-2024s-key-lessons-5824845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20election%20has%20been%20a%20moment%20of%20reckoning%20for%20everyone%20who%20wore%20arrogance%20as%20a%20second%20skin.%20It%20won't%20be%20hyperbolic%20to%20say%20that%20the%20humble%2C%20vulnerable%2C%20taken-for-granted%20voter%20had%20the%20last%20word%2C%20delivering%20a%20coup%20de%20grace.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Farrogance-evms-and-uttar-pradesh-election-2024s-key-lessons-5824845%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Knife%20attack%20on%20politician%20in%20German%20city%20days%20after%20fatal%20stabbing%20of%20police%20officer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717591620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-mannheim-germany-stabbing_6570529.jpg%3F20240531153539%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgermany-knife