0%20years%20so%20that%20you%20only%20replace%20it%20once.%20While%20this%20would%20cost%20you%20an%20additional%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20it%20will%20save%20you%20on%20recurring%20battery%20replacement%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBird%20droppings%20obstruct%20the%20sunlight%20that%20solar%20panels%20require%20to%20generate%20power.%20Therefore%2C%20you%20must%20routinely%20remove%20bird%20droppings%20from%20your%20solar%20setup.%20Install%20transponders%20that%20will%20transmit%20the%20live%20readings%20to%20you%20and%20show%20which%20panel%20is%20not%20generating%20enough%20electricity.%20Immediately%2C%20clean%20the%20panel%20to%20avoid%20malfunctions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDepending%20on%20the%20shadow%20analysis%2C%20you%20can%20recover%20the%20investment%20costs%20in%204-6%20years%20from%20the%20year%20of%20solar%20installation.%20Once%20you%20get%20your%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20get%20free%20power.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%227%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EApartment%20owners%20or%20tenants%20can%20install%20solar%20panels%20on%20their%20balconies%20provided%20they%20receive%20sufficient%20sunlight.%20A%20person%20living%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20and%2020th%20floor%20will%20receive%20different%20amounts%20of%20sunlight.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20building%20surrounding%20your%20view%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20sunlight%2C%20then%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20viable%20option%20as%20the%20efficiency%20levels%20will%20reduce.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%228%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConsider%20the%20area%20of%20coverage%20on%20your%20balcony.%20If%20your%20balcony%20is%2012-feet%20long%2C%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20place%203-4%20panels.%20You%20also%20require%20space%20to%20keep%20inverters%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%229%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20an%20apartment%20owner%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20to%20install%20solar%20panels%20on%20the%20terrace%20of%20your%20apartment%20complex%20and%20the%20society%20cannot%20refuse%20the%20request%2C%20provided%20there%20is%20a%20vacant%20space%20available%20on%20the%20rooftop.%20You%20can%20move%20the%20court%20if%20the%20society%20denies%20your%20request.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kiran%20suggests%20conducting%20shadow%20analysis%20to%20assess%20how%20much%20solar%20energy%20can%20be%20captured%20in%20a%20specific%20place.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1717590114-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352174%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKiran%20suggests%20conducting%20shadow%20analysis%20to%20assess%20how%20much%20solar%20energy%20can%20be%20captured%20in%20a%20specific%20place.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20if%20you%20live%20on%2C%20say%2C%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20a%2020-storey%20building%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20bringing%20the%20cable%20(wire)%20down%20from%20the%20terrace%20would%20be%20enormous.%20The%20add-ons%20could%20run%20into%20an%20additional%20Rs%201%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2211%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20you%20can%20opt%20for%20balconies%20which%20can%20minimise%20the%20cabling%20cost%20as%20the%20whole%20system%20would%20be%20drawn%20to%20your%20house%20including%20the%20net%20metre.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20viable%20proposition%20for%20apartment%20owners%20and%20tenants%20with%20rental%20agreements%20for%2010%20or%2015%20years.%20Tenants%20cannot%20remove%20the%20setup%20to%20take%20it%20somewhere%20else%20because%20it%20will%20again%20involve%20paperwork%20and%20installation%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2212%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20assume%20the%20monthly%20power%20expenses%20to%20be%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20installation%20and%20inverter%20(with%20a%2010-year%20warranty)%20to%20be%20Rs%201.5%20lakh.%20So%2C%20for%20a%2015-year%20contract%2C%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20will%20be%20generated%20only%20after%20five%20years%20and%20residents%20can%20avail%20of%20eight%20years%20of%20free%20electricity%20provided%20the%20inverter%20lasts%20for%20say%2013%20years.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20landlord%20will%20incur%20the%20capital%20cost%20for%20the%20new%20inverter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2213%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20on%20the%20terrace%20and%20balconies%2C%20Harish%20mentions%20that%20residents%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20metre%20and%20wiring%20expenses%20that%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Using%20balconies%20could%20not%20be%20very%20feasible%20if%20the%20energy%20generation%20will%20be%20small-scale%20compared%20to%20the%20requirement.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20balconies%2C%20there%20are%20safety%20risks%20from%20extreme%20weather%20events%20like%20lightning%20strikes%2C%20strong%20winds%2C%20and%20cyclones%20that%20can%20damage%20the%20panels.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKiran%20points%20out%