these%20calls%2024%C3%977.%20Some%20people%20donated%20huge%20sums%20of%20money%20to%20the%20foundation%2C%20while%20the%20organ%20pledges%20went%20up%20as%20well.%20It%20was%20very%20good%20publicity%20for%20our%20cause%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20relates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202449px)%20100vw%2C%202449px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FParticipating-in-Kaun-Banega-Crorepati_11zon-1717420744.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222449%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Participating%20in%20Kaun%20Banega%20Crorepati.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FParticipating-in-Kaun-Banega-Crorepati_11zon-1717420744.jpg%202449w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FParticipating-in-Kaun-Banega-Crorepati_11zon-1717420744-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FParticipating-in-Kaun-Banega-Crorepati_11zon-1717420744-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FParticipating-in-Kaun-Banega-Crorepati_11zon-1717420744-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FParticipating-in-Kaun-Banega-Crorepati_11zon-1717420744-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FParticipating-in-Kaun-Banega-Crorepati_11zon-1717420744-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FParticipating-in-Kaun-Banega-Crorepati_11zon-1717420744-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351945%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221632%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParticipating%20in%20Kaun%20Banega%20Crorepati.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20work%2C%20Dr%20Shroff%20and%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20have%20been%20felicitated%20with%20several%20awards%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20name%20a%20few%2C%20in%202015%2C%20the%20foundation%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20British%20Medical%20Association%20South%20Asia%20Award%20for%20establishing%20a%20cadaver%20programme%20in%20India.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20was%20given%20the%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20from%20Grant%20Thornton%20Sabera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Dr%20Shroff%20received%20the%20Dr%20K%20C%20G%20Verghese%C2%A0Excellence%C2%A0Awards%20for%20Community%20Service.%20The%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20also%20received%20the%20%E2%80%98Best%20NGO%20Award%E2%80%99%20in%202023%20from%20NOTTO%2C%20DGHS%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20National%20Organ%20Donation%20Day.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sunil%20Shroff%20receiving%20Dr%20K%20C%20G%20Verghese%20Excellence%20Awards%202023.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-300x134.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-500x223.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-768x343.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-1536x687.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-2048x915.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-150x67.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351941%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221144%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sunil%20Shroff%20receiving%20Dr%20K%20C%20G%20Verghese%20Excellence%20Awards%202023.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shroff%20is%20the%20Asia%20convenor%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Tribute%20to%20Life%20for%20Commonwealth%20Organ%20Donation%20Project%E2%80%99.%20He%20is%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20establishing%20the%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Organ%20Transplant%20Registry%E2%80%99%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Society%20of%20Organ%20Transplantation.%20This%20registry%2C%20a%20first%20in%20Asia%2C%20has%20been%20crucial%20for%20compiling%20data%20on%20kidney%20transplants%20in%20India%20and%20analysing%20their%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shroff%20believes%20that%20Indians%20are%20very%20emotional%20people%3B%20very%20giving%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20just%20some%20distrust%20with%20the%20healthcare%20system%20that%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%20More%20people%20will%20definitely%20come%20forward%20to%20donate%20the%20organs%20of%20loved%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20conviction.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20surgeon%2C%20I%20am%20deeply%20humbled%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20programme.%20During%20organ%20donations%2C%20I%20witness%20both%20ends%20of%20the%20spectrum%20%E2%80%93%20the%20profound%20grief%20of%20losing%20a%20loved%20one%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20joy%20and%20hope%20when%20a%20family%20member%20receives%20an%20organ.%20It%20truly%20embodies%20the%20cycle%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717422349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FLaunch-of-MOHAN-Foundation-in-1997-in-Chennai-1717420294.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Sunil%20Shroff%2C%20a%20renal%20transplant%20surgeon%2C%20established%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20in%201997%20after%20facing%20criticism%20abroad%20over%20the%20rising%20kidney%20transplant%20scams%20in%20India.%20His%20organisation%20educates%20and%20empowers%20people%20to%20take%20the%20organ%20donation%20pledge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Aruna%20Raghuram%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351914%2Forgan-donation-in-india-donor-mohan-foundation-dr-sunil-shroff-kbc-episode-kidney-transplant%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Just%20Rs%20350%2C%20%23DonateAnUmbrella%20to%20Street%20Vendors%20Working%20in%20Extreme%20Heatwaves%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20thinks%20like%20this%20for%20us%3B%20we%20have%20just%20gotten%20used%20to%20the%20heat%20every%20year.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20A%20Delhi%20Street%20Vendor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20working%20tirelessly%20under%20the%20scorching%20sun%20with%20no%20escape%20from%20the%20heat.%20This%20is%20the%20harsh%20reality%20for%20countless%20street%20vendors%2C%20rickshaw%20pullers%2C%20and%20labourers%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20hope%20arrives%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%E2%80%98Warriors%20Without%20a%20Cause%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20remarkable%20NGO%20founded%20by%20four%20young%20