20says.%20With%20her%20company%20Asan%2C%20she%20has%20helped%20over%2015%2C000%20women%20in%2060%20villages%20in%20Karnataka%20switch%20to%20menstrual%20cups%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cup%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20periods%20comfortable%20for%20every%20woman.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20rural%20women%2C%20menstrual%20cups%20can%20help%20make%20periods%20easier%20and%20healthier%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20foundation%20of%20Asan%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20when%20she%20was%2018%20to%20pursue%20her%20higher%20education.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20working%20as%20a%20management%20consultant%20in%20London%20and%20kept%20visiting%20home%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while.%20In%202016-17%2C%20the%20movie%20Padman%20was%20getting%20very%20popular%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20conversation%20around%20menstrual%20hygiene%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20of%20her%20visits%20during%20this%20time%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20that%20our%20cook%20was%20on%20leave%20and%20I%20had%20called%20to%20ask%20the%20reason.%20She%20told%20me%20that%20she%20had%20a%20rash%20due%20to%20using%20cheap%20sanitary%20pads.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurious%2C%20Ira%20asked%20her%20to%20bring%20the%20pad%20once%20she%20recovered%20to%20check%20its%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20never%20imagine%20using%20that%20pad%2C%20as%20it%20was%20very%20harsh%20and%20the%20material%20did%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20absorbent.%20It%20was%20at%20that%20time%20that%20I%20introduced%20her%20to%20menstrual%20cups.%20I%20was%20using%20one%20in%20the%20UK%20but%20there%20were%20no%20brands%20at%20the%20time%20selling%20them%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%