cup-use-environment-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarry%20menstrual%20cups%20for%20women%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20one%20point%2C%20I%20was%20carrying%2010-15%20menstrual%20cups%20on%20one%20trip%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20quite%20organic%2C%20I%20was%20distributing%20them%20among%20gardeners%20in%20the%20society%2C%20more%20domestic%20workers%20who%20heard%20about%20it%20etc.%20Fast%20forward%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20and%20went%20to%20study%20at%20Harvard.%20I%20was%20telling%20about%20my%20work%20in%20India%20to%20a%20professor%20who%20suggested%20that%20I%20should%20design%20my%20own%20cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20I%20developed%20the%20Asan%20cup%20by%20working%20with%20an%20engineer%20at%20the%20Harvard%20Innovation%20Lab.%20We%20thoroughly%20studied%20existing%20menstrual%20cups%20in%20great%20detail%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20highest%20quality%20cups%20available%20globally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20Asan%20different%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20research%20process%20and%20the%20hurdles%20she%20faced%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20product%20development%2C%20I%20faced%20the%20challenge%20of%20getting%20qualitative%20feedback%20on%20the%20usage%20of%20my%20cups%2C%20as%20I%20had%20distributed%20many%20cups%20throughout%20India.%20I%20needed%20detailed%20feedback%20about%20issues%20like%20leaking%2C%20overflowing%2C%20and%20comfort%2C%20but%20people%20weren%E2%80%99t%20sharing%20these%20openly%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20this%2C%20Ira%20included%20every%20single%20one%20of%20her%20friends%20in%20the%20user%20group.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20women%20across%20the%20US%20and%20UK%2C%20primarily%20contacts%20of%20my%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20willing%20to%20provide%20detailed%20feedback%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20challenge%20was%20the%20scepticism%20around%20people%20using%20menstrual%20cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20told%20me%20that%20India%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20ready%20for%20such%20a%20product%20and%20that%20women%20should%20stick%20to%20traditional%20methods.%20I%20overcame%20this%20challenge%20because%20I%20am%20a%20user%20of%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20myself%2C%20and%20it%20has%20transformed%20my%20life.%20I%20can%20sleep%20through%20the%20night%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261342%2Farpita-double-amputee-yoga-fitness-instructor-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20swim%2C%20do%20yoga%2C%20and%20run%20half%20a%20%3C%2Fa%3Emarathon%20comfortably.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20experience%2C%20along%20with%20the%20positive%20feedback%20from%20my%20early%20user%20group%E2%80%94including%20domestic%20workers%20and%20other%20women%20who%20adapted%20to%20the%20cup%20instantly%E2%80%94showed%20me%20that%20not%20only%20are%20women%20ready%20for%20this%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20calling%20out%20for%20it%20because%20the%20current%20products%20are%20of%20poor%20quality.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Ira%E2%80%99s%20personal%20experience%20and%20the%20experiences%20of%20women%20around%20her%20that%20gave%20her%20the%20conviction%20to%20challenge%20those%20who%20said%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20women%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20and%20insertable%20products%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20woman%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20need%20was%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asserts.%20Ira%20came%20out%20with%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20in%20the%20year%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-2-171707845