er%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F254622%2Flenovo-technology-agastya-international-meghshala-door-step-school-technoserve-medha-social-impact-innovation-oniline-education-c24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%20NGOs%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98Pratham%E2%80%99%20till%202022%20before%20she%20was%20selected%20for%20a%20fellowship%20at%20Stanford%20University%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20economist%20(Pavan)%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20his%20startup%20GIST%20Impact%2C%20a%20platform%20focusing%20on%20environmental%20economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20then%20regale%20you%20with%20stories%20about%20how%20the%20family%20set%20their%20sights%20on%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20green%20economy%2C%20all%20thanks%20to%20Mahima%E2%80%99s%20constant%20coaxing.%20The%20homestay%20has%20been%20privy%20to%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20moments%20%E2%80%94%20which%20include%20Pavan%20being%20awarded%20the%20%E2%80%98Tyler%20Prize%20for%20Environmental%20Achievement%E2%80%99%20in%202020%2C%20and%20Vinati%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%98East%20or%20West%3A%20An%20NRI%20Mother%E2%80%99s%20Manual%20on%20How%20to%20Bring%20up%20Desi%20Children%20Overseas%E2%80%99%20getting%20global%20acclaim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20family%20may%20now%20be%20settled%20across%20the%20globe%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20Vinati%20lives%20in%20London%2C%20Pavan%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20Mahima%20in%20England%2C%20and%20Ashima%20in%20Seattle%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reverence%20for%20the%20environment%20ties%20them%20together.%20It%20lies%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20everything%20they%20undertake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20the%20O%E2%80%99Land%20Plantation%20is%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20stunning%20landscapes%20and%20the%20desire%20to%20not%20let%20them%20be%20infiltrated%20with%20irresponsible%20tourism%20that%20attracted%20the%20couple%20in%202007%20when%20they%20set%20out%20to%20buy%20the%20land.%20%E2%80%9CPavan%20fe